'''Hugh Spight''' was a puppeteer who worked on [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']], although his name was misspelled as "Hugh Spirit" in the credits. Before working on Star Wars, he worked on [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Great_Muppet_Caper The Great Muppet Caper].

